Huawei has launched a range of new deals on smartphones, smartwatches, and digital accessories on the Huawei Online Store. The sale is in celebration of Huawei Joburg Day, and gives shoppers access to big savings on the latest devices. A standout deal from the sale is the “buy-get-one-free” offer on the Huawei Watch Fit. Shoppers who purchase a Huawei Watch Fit will get an additional Watch Fit for free. The Huawei Watch Fit packs a range of advanced exercise features, a long battery life, and a modern and sleek design – which will be a hit amongst fitness enthusiasts. A selection of the best deals from the Huawei Joburg Day Sale are listed below. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-372568" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100420eSpace.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="637" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100420eSpace.jpg 772w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100420eSpace-402x400.jpg 402w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100420eSpace-432x430.jpg 432w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100420eSpace-768x764.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-372564" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100357eSpace.jpg" alt="Huawei" width="640" height="634" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100357eSpace.jpg 775w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100357eSpace-404x400.jpg 404w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100357eSpace-434x430.jpg 434w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Huawei-100357eSpace-768x761.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="a